{"tid":505762,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"懷疑男朋友外遇","createTime":"2017-12-21T13:09:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-21T14:34:31.000Z","uid":134999,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"28cc4448982c4c20189e6290de8428eaba39724e","tid":505762,"uid":134999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T13:09:05.000Z","msg":"我同男朋友拍左三年拖，平時一個星期都有兩三日上佢屋企訓，但上個禮拜一佢開始對我失去興趣，我係屋企著佢件tee下身真空佢望都冇望我，之後我話我想要啊，之後佢就話屌咁撚麻煩架<br />\n幫佢含左十分鐘佢都未係好硬，於是我就話不如你食粒藥啦，佢又無啦啦發嬲，又話我鬆又話我含得唔好，仲要我喊到豬頭咁佢都冇氹返我，走左上床訓教<br />\n前兩日我仲聽到佢chok住把聲兼陰聲細氣咁話要餵人，我聽到就知咩事，即刻check佢手機，原來個衰佬晚晚同人曖昧。<br />\n我唔知應該點算，好難得先得到兩方家長同意比我地同居，我地又係同一間中學畢業，下年仲諗住去荷蘭注冊，我又好唔捨得佢，各位巴絲有咩辦法先可以令佢返黎我身邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c6e644996c44f215ba460f4f1431ae781005e1a","tid":505762,"uid":828,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T13:13:55.000Z","msg":"今次作得幾好 得荷蘭呢個提示<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91f96fc062707330f57c85579bf0bc1a2567abeb","tid":505762,"uid":120214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T13:17:38.000Z","msg":"this"},{"pid":"b4481f7077fa841a48ed4dcd69dc17b245e539aa","tid":505762,"uid":156331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T14:16:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"99514882d9cb53d02c3309516032fff20ce1321f","tid":505762,"uid":147789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T14:20:14.000Z","msg":"三個月之前你話拍咗年半 依家又變三年<br />\n你到底幾多個男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc5701f2c3d778559d083ab895e8136775da74de","tid":505762,"uid":21664,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T14:21:15.000Z","msg":"你講呀！你讀咩中學呀屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dc4d0c8a1131cc429c8b11bda818b389a53142e","tid":505762,"uid":134999,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T14:34:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你講呀！你讀咩中學呀屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n英華"}]}